      </infoLinks>
    </selectionEntry>
    <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Relics (Refrence)" hidden="false" id="51ab-3977-5f4d-9601" sortIndex="-3">
      <profiles>
        <profile name="1 Cuirass of Sacrifice" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="d3ee-6a00-f361-055a">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">This unit gains Resilient 6+. While this unit is within 6” of one or more friendly units, add 1 to Resilient Rolls made for this unit.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="2 Grand Master’s Nemesis Banner" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="b863-7d87-ad5f-bc70">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this unit’s Move step, each visible enemy unit within 2D6” suffers 6 SW.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="3 Seal of Forbiddance" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="9b3f-a1cd-4e03-f6e6">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">During this unit’s turn, each time an enemy unit suffers X SW, you may instead have that unit suffer X Suppression. Additionally, while enemy units with Suppressed are within 3” of this unit, those units cannot be selected for Activation unless their controlling player has no other units available for Activation.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="4 The Soul Glaive" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="787d-fb9d-d79d-c5a2">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this unit is Activated, select one model in this unit. Then, until the End step, the selected model gains the selected weapon:</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="5 Augury Malifica" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="8f82-c56a-cbae-d162">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">For each attack this unit makes for a weapon with Nemesis, a Hit Roll of 6 causes an additional hit. After an enemy unit’s Move step, if that unit is visible to this unit, roll a D6. On a 5+, make ranged attacks targeting that enemy unit (if able).</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="6 Domina Liber Daemonica" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="6476-7326-8c38-270d">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this unit’s Attacks step, you may select an enemy unit visible to and within 6” of this unit. The selected enemy unit suffers 3D6+X Suppression where X is this unit&apos;s Psyker X. Then, if the selected enemy unit has Suppressed, that enemy unit must be removed from the battlefield and placed into the reserves.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="4 The Soul Glaive (Weapon)" typeId="2dff-53d0-6d25-8c59" typeName="Weapon" hidden="false" id="7fcc-e849-5205-050e">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Tp" typeId="6c1c-7d1d-c8b0-33ec">ML</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="A" typeId="13c5-f234-c120-afc3">6+X</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="WS" typeId="459f-6890-e77f-b62f">2+</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="S" typeId="571c-0471-2614-c57c">6</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="D" typeId="c2c0-3714-05e2-65a0">2</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Abilities" typeId="d93f-70ee-72bc-5ef9">Nemesis X is equal to the total Psyker X from your destroyed units (if you have two destroyed units with Psyker 2, A is equal to 10).</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <constraints>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="edd3-45c6-215b-3072" includeChildSelections="false"/>
      </constraints>
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink name="Configuration" hidden="false" id="b477-aa5d-7d52-d3ac" targetId="9cd6-0442-3f35-6b52" primary="true"/>
      </categoryLinks>
    </selectionEntry>
    <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Psychic Powers (Refrence)" hidden="false" id="5d41-be7e-2be6-c477" sortIndex="-4">
      <profiles>
        <profile name="2 Gate of Infinity" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="b65c-a53e-f4b1-6b4c">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Remove this unit from the battlefield and place it into reserves. Then, Deploy it anywhere in the battlefield at least 3D6” away from enemy models.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="1 Summon" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="198f-050e-6ca5-106c">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select a friendly Grey Knights unit in the battlefield or in reserves. If the selected unit is in the battlefield, remove that unit from the battlefield and place it into reserves. Then, Deploy the selected unit wholly within 6&quot; of this unit, outside of engagement range of enemy models.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="3 Hallow Ground" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="a156-ce34-fc8a-57a4">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Until the next time this unit is Activated or dies, for each melee attack an enemy unit makes targeting this unit, this unit gains Resilient 5+ for that attack.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="4 Shrouding" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="0eec-f502-7dbe-33e8">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Until the next time this unit is Activated or dies, for each ranged attack that targets this unit or a friendly Grey Knights unit that is within 2” of this unit, add 1 to the D6 roll of Santic Aegis for that attack. Each attack cannot be affected by this psychic power more than once.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="5 Purifying Flame" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="67d9-410a-24c8-4403">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select 1 enemy unit visible to this unit within 8”. Then, the selected unit suffers D3+X SW where X is this unit’s current Health.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="6 Argent Psybolt" typeId="6406-cf2b-ec5b-c7e6" typeName="Psychic Power" hidden="false" id="e1a5-f603-48b1-5aab">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4b9e-dc73-b312-b42d">Select any weapon with Nemesis in this unit. Once this turn, after any successful wound roll for a weapon with Nemesis, the target of that attack suffers X SW where X is equal to the highest result of your last Psychic Test.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink name="Configuration" hidden="false" id="bfe2-5cc2-843e-1b47" targetId="9cd6-0442-3f35-6b52" primary="true"/>
      </categoryLinks>
      <constraints>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="78bd-2543-568a-fa60" includeChildSelections="false"/>
      </constraints>
    </selectionEntry>
    <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Grand Master" hidden="false" id="104a-d6af-9b28-1f1d" sortIndex="1">
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink name="Leaders" hidden="false" id="9abe-f1b3-9268-a427" targetId="2886-2afd-f65f-9d8e" primary="true"/>
        <categoryLink name="Infantry" hidden="false" id="bc28-a2c0-bf53-422a" targetId="205c-3072-067b-d808" primary="false"/>
      </categoryLinks>
      <profiles>
        <profile name="Grand Master" typeId="a706-96eb-fcae-b696" typeName="Unit" hidden="false" id="9bd6-09b8-f0a0-77e3">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="M" typeId="c06e-b1a2-0f87-fe2f">5&quot;</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="T" typeId="a6ad-d820-8495-f5b0">-</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Sv" typeId="9b7f-0dde-683f-6844">2+</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="H" typeId="18e4-1bf9-a9b8-1e50">3</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Rv" typeId="411f-3942-6dc0-7c06">-</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Leader" typeId="55da-e0a0-1fa3-2d1c" typeName="Leader" hidden="false" id="95ba-06f2-9f46-35c9">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Must Attach to" typeId="2c63-5e3f-9132-459d">This unit must attach to either:
a) GREY KNIGHT TERMINATORS
